Gallagher, Respondent, v. Grand Trunk Ry. Co. of Canada, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. March, 1889.) For former report, see ante, 581.

Argued before Barker, P. J., and Dwight and Ma#omber, JJ.

B. O. Sptrague, for appellant. Martin W. Cook, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed for the reason stated in the opinions in the •case of Jennings v. Railway Co., 5 N. Y. Supp. 140.
